        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 3: Eligibility for release on licence of terrorist prisoners: Scotland</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 4: Disapplication of existing release provisions: Scotland</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 5: Setting of licence conditions for terrorist prisoners: England and Wales</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 6: Consequential amendments relating to transitional cases: England and Wales</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 7: Other consequential amendments: England and Wales</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 8: Transitional provision for terrorist prisoners subject to supervised release orders: S...</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 9: Consequential amendments: Scotland</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Section 10: Extent, commencement, transitory provision and short title</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Schedule 1: Terrorist Offences carrying restricted eligibility for release on licence</inline></tocItem>
        <tocItem href="#section_5" level="3"><inline name="tocHeading">Schedule 2: Terrorist offences carrying restricted eligibility for release on licence: Scotland</inline></tocItem>
