            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>58.</num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The provisions in this Act form part of the law of England and Wales. Some extend and apply to England and Wales, and some extend and apply to Scotland. </span></p>
            </blockContainer>
